      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so my doctor prescribed me some diazepam to help me sleep cause i havent been sleeping well lately. but i was wondering if its okay to have like a small glass of red wine with it? i feel like the wine might actually help the pill work a bit better so i can pass out faster. is that safe for light use?",
